      "description": "$19,500 - Honest older car in fair condition and priced where it should be. It is complete, usable, and presentable enough to enjoy as-is, but it shows its age with visible cosmetic wear, imperfections to the paint and trim, and a generally driver-quality appearance inside and out. This is not a restored or show-level example, but it is a straightforward, honest car for someone who wants an affordable entry point and is comfortable with an older vehicle that has seen regular use.",
