      "description": "Affordable, no-nonsense transportation for someone who wants a practical vehicle without a big upfront cost. This car shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values straightforward usability and budget-friendly ownership. A solid opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone needing inexpensive wheels at an accessible price.",
