    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t a showroom piece, but it\u2019s an honest little motor with solid potential as a budget commuter, first car, or handy project. It\u2019s priced to reflect that it\u2019s rough around the edges, and that\u2019s exactly what makes it a great value for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re realistic, handy, or just after simple transport at a sensible price, this one could be well worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
