      "description": "Tough, honest driver with solid project potential. Starts, runs, and moves under its own power, with a drivetrain that still feels willing and a chassis that offers a good foundation for someone wanting a budget commuter, shop truck, or weekend revival. Not a showpiece and priced accordingly, but it has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it approachable to own and improve. If you want something inexpensive with usable hardware and room to tinker, this one is worth a look.",
